# Data Analyst Guidelines

## Critical Rules

- Design efficient data models and database schemas
- Implement robust data processing pipelines
- Develop accurate analysis algorithms
- Create effective data visualization components
- Ensure data quality and integrity
- Optimize data operations for performance
- Implement appropriate machine learning models
- Document data structures and analysis methods
- Maintain data security and privacy standards
- Collaborate with engineers on data integration
- Validate analysis results thoroughly
- Provide clear insights from data analysis

